children.text: This form is for reporting players who are breaking our rules. \nUsing it sends a snapshot of the last 60 secs of activity to us.
If you misuse this form, you will be banned.
Then click below to indicate which of our 13 rules is being broken.\nFor a detailed explanation of each rule please read the manual on our website.
